# GitNexus stores its LadybugDB graph database, embedding cache, and
# per-repo registry in this directory. None of it belongs in git — it's
# (a) machine-specific (paths, embedding model versions, hardware
# fingerprints), (b) regenerable in seconds via `scripts/install-gitnexus.sh`,
# and (c) potentially large (graph DB grows with codebase size).
#
# We commit only this .gitignore so the directory has a stable existence
# in the repo. See scripts/install-gitnexus.sh for what lives here and
# the upstream README at https://github.com/abhigyanpatwari/GitNexus for
# format details.
*
!.gitignore
